Lamplight - The Bandit Guild of Skyrim
/******************************/
/* Lamplight Beta 03          
/* By: Brewskie (Fragginborn) 
/* 7/3/12                    
/******************************/

Voices:

Pengae............... Ingenue
All other voices ... Brewskie

If you would like to voice some of the characters in Lamplight please visit the Voice Actors thread at the mod\'s web site: http://lamplight.pcgamingnetwork.com/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=19

--------------------------------------------------------

The premise of the mod is to create a new guild of Bandit outlaws. They are all over Skyrim but where do they come from? What\'s their story?

I hope to answer those questions, er... at least make something up :)

Lamplight - The Bandit Guild is now in beta. This means that the heart of the story and quests are now going to be created.

To read the story line there will be a special post at the mod web site link above.

Even though the mod is in beta nothing is finalized, including the lighting, buildings or anything else. Anything can change as it is being developed.

The mod starts with a visit to the Southern entrance to the town of Lamplight where a group of bandits are at guard.

The player is informed that they are not welcome and will attack of the player doesn\'t leave.

As the player walks away he is confronted by \"Scurrvy\" who gives the player instructions on how to get in to Lamplight.

Once the player follows the instructions given by Surrvy the bandits guarding the entrance will have disappeared. This is only temporary as there will be a new confrontation with these bandits in the next release of the mod (Beta 3)

You can get in to Lamplight after the initial quest. If you would like to see most of the characters that will later be in the quests within Lamplight go in to the Tavern. BTW...you can disregard the dragon sitting on the Tavern...he will be in one of the quests later in the game.

Remember, the more input I get from the people using the mod the better I can make it. So please give me your thoughts!

/****************/
/* Gaming Notes */
/****************/

While the bandits greet the player as I intended they sometimes take a while to actually walk up to the player. I am working on finding a solution to this.

When the initial greetings are finished the player finds themselves in a certain place. I left the door unlocked so you can get out and into lamplight. The next version will be 1st quest for the guild.

/****************************/
/* Conflict With Other Mods */
/****************************/

Too early to know. But unless some other mod is using the same space in Tamriel there should be no problems.


/****************/
/* Known Issues */
/****************/

Please let me know if you discover any problems.


/****************/
/* Installation */
/****************/

Copy lamplight.esp, lamplight.bsl & lamplight.bsa from the downloaded archive to your Skyrim Data folder.


/****************/
/* UnInstall */
/****************/

If you have an earlier version of Lamplight please delete the following folders before installing this version.
Hopefully this will be the last change in installation methods.
Before you uninstall please leave the interior of Lamplight Town, if your character is now there, and create a save point.

To uninstall delete the following files from the Date folder:

lamplight.esp
lamplight.bsl
lamplight.bsa


